      "text": [
        "2219 - وَ كَانَ اَلْحُسَيْنُ بْنُ عَلِيٍّ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَمْشِي وَ تُسَاقُ مَعَهُ اَلْمَحَامِلُ وَ اَلرِّحَالُ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.2219 - Imam Hussain ibn Ali (as) used to walk while the camels carrying the provisions and supplies were driven alongside him."
